    "Therefore, the model needs to accurately identify 'cardiomegaly' for both these two different inputs.",
    "As shown in Table 1, for the report summarization task, we can compute the variance in model performance on the two datasets, IU-Xray and MIMIC-CXR (collected from different hospitals and regions, thus having different expression habits), to obtain the robustness of the model on this task.",
